---

<section class="relative w-full px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 xl:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl lg:max-w-screen-xl">
        <Image
            class="mx-auto"
            src={MBAAPPTimeline}
            alt="MBA Admissions Consulting Timeline"
            width={MBAAPPTimeline.width}
            height={MBAAPPTimeline.height}
        />
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl text-center py-8">
            <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? 'MBA 지원 마감일 및 결과 발표일 (2024-2025 입학전형)' : 'MBA application deadlines and decision release dates for the 2024–2025 admissions cycle'"></span>
        </h2>

        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
                <thead class="bg-gray-50">
                    <tr>
                        <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                            <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '경영대학원' : 'Business School'"></span>
                        </th>
                        <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                            <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '지원 마감일' : 'Application Deadlines'"></span>
                        </th>
                        <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                            <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '결과 발표일' : 'Decision Release Dates'"></span>
                        </th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200">
                    {businessSchools?.map((school) => (
                        <tr>
                            <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">
                                <span x-data x-text={`$store.language === 'ko' ? '${school.nameKr}' : '${school.name}'`}></span>
                            </td>
                            <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-500">
                                {school.applicationDeadlines?.map((deadline) => (
                                    <div>{deadline}</div>
                                ))}
                            </td>
                            <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap text-sm text-gray-500">
                                {school.decisionReleaseDates?.map((date) => (
                                    <div>{date}</div>
                                ))}
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    ))}
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-8">
                <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '에세이 팁' : 'Essay Tips'"></span>
            </h2>
            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-500">
                <p class="mb-6 lg:text-lg text-base text-gray-600">
                    <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '1) 직장 경력' : '1) Work Experience'"></span>
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6 lg:text-lg text-base text-gray-600">
                    <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' 
                        ? '일반적으로는 최소 3년 정도의 직장 경력을 요구 합니다. 삼성전자, 유명 컨설팅, IB 등 해외에서도 모두 아는 직장 경력이 있다면 아무래도 유리할 수 있습니다. MBA 도 결국 졸업 후 취업이 잘 될 것 같은 사람을 뽑는데, 기존 직장 경력이 좋은 사람이 아무래도 MBA 이후 취업에 더 유리할 수 밖에 없기 때문입니다.'
                        : 'Generally, a minimum of 3 years of work experience is required. Having experience at globally recognized companies like Samsung Electronics, prestigious consulting firms, or investment banks can be advantageous. MBA programs ultimately seek candidates with strong post-graduation employment prospects, and those with impressive work experience tend to have better job opportunities after MBA.'"></span>
                </p>
                
                <p class="mb-6 lg:text-lg text-base text-gray-600">
                    <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '2) 이력서, 에세이, 추천서' : '2) Resume, Essays, and Letters of Recommendation'"></span>
                </p>
                <p class="mb-6 lg:text-lg text-base text-gray-600">
                    <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko'
                        ? '보통 GMAT과 토플 점수를 확보하게 되면, 실질적인 Application절차를 시작합니다. 이때 필요한 Package가 이력서 (Resume), 에세이 (Essay), 지원서 (Application Form), 추천서 (Recommendation Letter) 입니다. 이 4가지 지원 패키지를 학교별로 갖추는 데도 상당히 시간이 소요되기 때문에, GMAT과 토플은 늦어도 4월 이전에 끝내고, 5월 부터는 학교별 지원 패키지를 준비하는 데 시간을 쓰는 것을 추천 드립니다.'
                        : 'Once you secure your GMAT and TOEFL scores, you can begin the actual application process. The required package includes a Resume, Essays, Application Form, and Letters of Recommendation. Since preparing these four application components for each school takes considerable time, we recommend completing GMAT and TOEFL by April at the latest and dedicating time from May onwards to prepare school-specific application packages.'"></span>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-16">
            <div class="space-y-8">
                {essayTips.map((tip) => (
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                            {tip.id}) <span x-data={`{ title: ${JSON.stringify(tip.title)}, titleEn: ${JSON.stringify(tip.titleEn)} }`} x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? title : titleEn"></span>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 lg:text-lg text-md">
                            <span x-data={`{ description: ${JSON.stringify(tip.description)}, descriptionEn: ${JSON.stringify(tip.descriptionEn)} }`} x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? description : descriptionEn"></span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                ))}
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-x-auto">
                <div class="min-w-[800px]">
                    <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
                        <thead class="bg-gray-50">
                            <tr>
                                <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                                    <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '시험 영역' : 'Exam Section'"></span>
                                </th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                                    <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '시간 제한' : 'Time Limit'"></span>
                                </th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                                    <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '문항 수' : 'Questions'"></span>
                                </th>
                                <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                                    <span x-data x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? '점수 범위' : 'Score Range'"></span>
                                </th>
                            </tr>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200">
                            {gmatDetails.map((detail) => (
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap lg:text-lg text-md text-gray-900">
                                        <span x-data={`{ sectionKr: '${detail.sectionKr}', section: '${detail.section}' }`} x-text="$store.language === 'ko' ? sectionKr : section"></span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap lg:text-lg text-md text-gray-500">{detail.time}</td>
                                    <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap lg:text-lg text-md text-gray-500">{detail.questions}</td>
                                    <td class="px-6 py-4 whitespace-nowrap lg:text-lg text-md text-gray-500">{detail.score}</td>
                                </tr>
                            ))}
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>